        <title>[Git] branch가 자세히 뭘까?</title>
        <link>https://choiseungwoo98.github.io/p/git-branch%EA%B0%80-%EC%9E%90%EC%84%B8%ED%9E%88-%EB%AD%98%EA%B9%8C/</link>
